    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368130/extras/887a2c9128baf162d41cd6a2e1026794.poster.avif?t=1744657301\" width=576 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368130/extras/887a2c9128baf162d41cd6a2e1026794.webm?t=1744657301\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Can you manage, Sorkin, to finally destroy the evil pumpkin wizard and defeat all his undead followers? So far, no living being has succeeded, but are you perhaps something special? A unique hero with extraordinary abilities?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368130/extras/4a41de27d3f73afa56e3e3977b1a4884.poster.avif?t=1744657301\" width=570 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368130/extras/4a41de27d3f73afa56e3e3977b1a4884.webm?t=1744657301\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>But to get to Sorkin in the first place, you have to go through the Land of the Dead. The dead, who have already stopped numerous ones before you from reaching Sorkin. Fight your way through the different levels and get closer to Sorkin over and over again. Roam through the Overworld and try to leave all the undead behind.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368130/extras/dea9e6c04008753e774fb30684a11e43.poster.avif?t=1744657301\" width=570 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2368130/extras/dea9e6c04008753e774fb30684a11e43.webm?t=1744657301\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>But it's not that easy because the undead also learn and become stronger. To keep up with them, you have to collect their souls and then use them in the shop to upgrade your equipment, such as your sword or backpack, and always maintain the upper hand in the fight against Sorkin and his followers.",
